properties.property: function npc_handler(npc, ch) do_message(npc, ch, "Do you want me to lift you to the upper level?") local v = do_choice(npc, ch, "Sure", "Not yet!") if v == 1 then tmw.chr_warp(ch, 2, 87 * 32 + 16, 99 * 32 + 16) end end

function npc_handler(npc, ch) local g = tonumber(get_quest_var(npc, ch, "005_chest")) if not g then do_message(npc, ch, "Would you try to open it?") local v = do_choice(npc, ch, "Yup", "Nope") if v == 1 then if tmw.chr_inv_change(ch, 537, -3, 536, 1) then do_message(npc, ch, "You opened it and found a short sword!") tmw.chr_set_quest(ch, "005_chest", 1) else do_message(npc, ch, "It seems that this is not the right key...") end end else do_message(npc, ch, "You already opened this chest.") end end
